    "en": {
      "title": "The preparation of the Parliament for the new assembly",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A rehearsal for the ceremonial opening of the third session of the Ninth Parliament was held today at the Parliament complex.",
        "Officers of the armed forces and police, students of Colombo Devi Girls' College and others were present.",
        "Mr. Narendra Fernando, Sergeant-at-Arms of the Parliament, said that arrangements have been made to hold the President's visit to the Parliament as a formal ceremony and accordingly there will be no salutes and motorcades."
      ],
